import React from "react";
import styled from "styled-components";
import { Container } from "react-bootstrap";
import { Panel, PanelGroup, Paragraph } from "rsuite";

const Styles = styled.div``;
export const Contact = () => (
  <Styles>
    <Container>
      <PanelGroup accordion bordered>
        <Panel header="Deniz Taksi Nedir?" defaultExpanded>
          <Paragraph />
        </Panel>
        <Panel header="Deniz Taksi Güvenli Midir?">
          <Paragraph />
        </Panel>
        <Panel header="Deniz Taksi Karşılama Hizmeti Nedir?">
          <Paragraph />
        </Panel>
        <Panel header="Deniz Taksi'de Ödeme Nasıl Alınır?">
          <Paragraph />
        </Panel>
        <Panel header="Deniz Taksi'de Yeme-İçme Koşulları Nelerdir?">
          <Paragraph />
        </Panel>
      </PanelGroup>
    </Container>
  </Styles>
);
